Title: 095: From Uber to Data Science – A Winner’s Journey
Description:
In this episode of the SuperDataScience Podcast, I chat with the Regional Operations Manager at Uber, Josh Kennedy. You will hear what it's like to work at Uber, you will learn about the importance of job satisfaction and quality of life, and you will also hear about the role of ideas vs. execution.


If you enjoyed this episode, check out show notes, resources, and more at www.superdatascience.com/95
